ChangeLog
=========

This is the ChangeLog file for OpenTracker. This file is automatically
generated. Entries are in reversed chronological order.

See http://www.red-bean.com/cvs2cl/ for information about the
cvs2cl script used to generate this file.

============================================================================

2003-03-28 15:48  reitmayr

	* src/common/CommonNodeFactory.cxx, src/common/CommonNodeFactory.h,
	src/common/EllipsoidTransformNode.h,
	src/common/GKTransformNode.cxx, src/common/GKTransformNode.h,
	src/common/Makefile.am, data/opentracker.dtd, data/test.xml,
	opentracker.dsp:
	
	added filter node for transformations to the Gausz - Krueger
	coordinates for Austrian maps. This allows to really use the GPS
	data with our local data.

