2003-03-25 12:05  kaufmann

	* src/input/: P5GloveModule.cxx, P5GloveModule.h:
	
	Button activation implemented with P5 glove.  By bending the index
	finger, button state 1 is set.	Therefore clicking and dragging is
	supported.

