2003-03-21 15:52  kaufmann

	* src/input/: P5GloveModule.cxx, P5GloveModule.h, P5GloveSource.h:
	
	New P5Glove Module. Supports the P5 Glove, sends position and
	orientation of the whole hand correctly, no button support is
	implemented yet.  Finger positions are not calculated seperately
	yet.

