2003-03-14 03:36  tamer

	* cfg/m4/: ace.m4, artoolkit.m4, xerces.m4:
	
	added stb_ac_*_rpath flag to allow libtool to encode the path to
	the library so that the dynamic linker/loader is able to find the
	library without having to set the LD_LIBRARY_PATH environment if
	the library is not installed in the linker search path on the
	system.

2003-02-22 01:37  tamer

	* lib/lib.txt:
	
	now obsolete, as directory is not empty anymore.

2003-02-18 03:12  tamer

	* INSTALL, configure.ac, opentracker_env.sh, cfg/m4/libtool.m4,
	cfg/m4/xerces.m4, src/core/ConfigurationParser.cxx,
	src/core/ConfigurationParser.h, src/core/Context.cxx,
	src/core/DOMTreeErrorReporter.h, src/core/Node.cxx,
	src/core/Node.h, src/core/State.h, src/core/StringTable.h,
	src/core/ThreadModule.h, src/misc/xml/XMLWriter.cxx,
	src/misc/xml/XMLWriter.h:
	
	updated sources to use xerces_2_2. necessary namespace handling is
	done using macros that xerces provides. Node.h exports those macros
	again conditionally so that 3rd party libs like Studierstube use
	the right symbols and don't depend on xerces like we always had it.
	
	some cleanups regarding gcc3 compiler warnings (reodering issues).
	
	updated libtool to 1.4.3 to be consistent with the Studierstube
	build system.
	
	improved xerces.m4 to output a more informative error string.

